@startuml
skin plantuml2

actor Client
participant "Web Server / Router" as WebServer
participant "Users API Service\n(external)" as UsersAPI
database "SQL Database\n(for Users API Service)" as Database

Client -> WebServer : GET /api/users (proxied or routed)
WebServer -> UsersAPI : GET /api/users
UsersAPI -> Database : EXECUTE SQL\nSELECT id,name,email FROM users WHERE active = true
Database --> UsersAPI : rows[]
UsersAPI --> WebServer : JSON { users: [...] }
WebServer --> Client : HTTP 200 JSON

@enduml
